item.title: Jacques Dutronc
item.description: Jacques Dutronc is a French singer, songwriter, guitarist, composer, and actor. He has been married to singer Françoise Hardy since 30 March 1981 and the two have a son. He also has been a longtime songwriting collaborator with Jacques Lanzmann. Some of Dutronc's best-known hits include 'Il est cinq heures, Paris s'éveille', 'Le Responsable', and 'Les Cactus'.
